getPSDEDataQueryCodeConds.name: 查询条件

getPSDEDataQueryCodeConds.customCond:
(t1.id IN (
SELECT
	t.product 
FROM
	zt_projectproduct t 
WHERE
	t.project IN (
SELECT
	t3.root 
FROM
	zt_team t3 
WHERE
	t3.account = #{srf.sessioncontext.srfloginname} 
	AND t3.type = 'project' 
	) 
	) or  t1.acl = 'open')
